 193:../../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/hid/disp/display.h **** /** This class is intended as a intermediary class for your actual implementation of the OneBitGrap
 194:../../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/hid/disp/display.h ****  *  interface. It uses the CRTP design pattern where the template argument is the child class. It p
 195:../../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/hid/disp/display.h ****  *  implementations for most of the functions, except DrawPixel(), Update() and Fill(), which you'l
 196:../../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/hid/disp/display.h ****  *  to provide in your child class.
 197:../../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/hid/disp/display.h ****  *  The main goal of this class is to provide common drawing functions without relying on massive a
 198:../../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/hid/disp/display.h ****  *  virtual function calls that would result in a performance loss. To achieve this, any drawing fu
 199:../../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/hid/disp/display.h ****  *  is implemented here and internally calls other drawing functions (e.g. DrawRect() which interna
 200:../../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/hid/disp/display.h ****  *  DrawPixel() and DrawLine()) makes these calls via the qualified name of these functions to expl
 201:../../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/hid/disp/display.h ****  *  suppress the virtual dispatch mechanism like this:
 202:../../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/hid/disp/display.h ****  * 
 203:../../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/hid/disp/display.h ****  *      ChildType::DrawPixel(...); // no virtual function call; direct call into the child class fu
 204:../../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/hid/disp/display.h ****  *  
 205:../../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/hid/disp/display.h ****  *  To create a custom OneBitGraphicsDisplay implementation, you can 
 206:../../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/hid/disp/display.h ****  *  A) inherit from OneBitGraphicsDisplay directly and provide all the drawing functions yourself
 207:../../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/hid/disp/display.h ****  *  B) Inherit from OneBitGraphicsDisplayImpl and only provide DrawPixel(), Fill() and Update()
ARM GAS  C:\Users\skipi\AppData\Local\Temp\ccF95xUK.s 			page 14


 208:../../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/hid/disp/display.h ****  *     like this:
